divs: Sighting DetailsI sent this picture in to you guys before, unedited. I don't have the number of the file I was given. But here is the magnified version. This is the best I could do with the photo enhancement program I have. If you still have the origional, maybe you can do better. I used the telephoto feature. It was a long distance away. It also was cloaked by a cloud. I used the contrast to show the shape of the object. Now that I know how bright these suckers are, I can spot them. They move pretty fast. I'm lucky to get a snapshot. Everyone I showed the photo to, just couldn't see what I saw, so I cropped it down.
